AMMAN, September 2 (Xinhua) -- A visiting Palestinian official
today brushed aside the Israeli claim to ease the closure on the
West Bank and Gaza Strip as "empty and meaningless."
</P>
<P>
Israel is still imposing a "collective" punishment on most
Palestinians, said Palestinian Minister of Information Yasser Abed
Rabbo after meeting with Jordanian Prime Minister Abdul-Salam
Majali this afternoon.
