<TEXT>
<P>
LAUNDA, September 2 (Xinhua) -- Forty U.S. entreprenurs from 31
enterprises will visit Angola from September 8 to 11, Jose
Cardoso, the Director for Trade Promotion in the Angola Industry
and Commerce Commission said here today.
</P>
<P>
Jose Cardoso told the press that the U.S. entreprenurs' delegation
comprising 31 enterprises involving construction, finance,
energy, communication, petroleum, agricultrure, fishery, trade
and telecommunications, will pay a visit to Angola with an aim to
explore the possibility for expanding trade between the two
countreis and strengthening cooperation between the enterprisers of
the two countries.
</P>
