will hold discussions with Angolan cabinet ministers and will go
to the northern Cabinda Province and southern Huila Province to
meet Angolan enterprisers in the two provinces.
</P>
<P>
This will be the first U.S.entrepreneurs delegation to visit
Angola since diplomatic relations between the two countries were
established in 1993. 
