<HEADLINE> Jordan Not Optimistic About Albright's Trip </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
AMMAN, September 3 (Xinhua) -- Jordan was not optimistic about
U.S. Secretary of State Madeleine Albright's upcoming Middle East
trip scheduled on September 9, Jordanian Prime Minister
Abdul-Salam Majali said today.
</P>
<P>
Jordan was also not optimistic about the result of Albright's
meeting with Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu, the
Jordanian prime minister told a press conference here.
</P>
<P>
