addition to the strong dollar, the psychological factor might also
have fueled the baht slump.
</P>
<P>
He called on the public to remain calm.
</P>
<P>
The baht Tuesday was once traded at more than 35 baht against
the dollar, setting the previous record.
</P>
<P>
Analysts said that the opposition's announcement today to file
an impeachment against Prime Minister Chavalit Yongchaiyudh on
September 8 might also be among the factors that drove the baht to
tumble.  
</P>
