<HEADLINE> Ukrainian Economist Praises China's Economic Way </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KIEV, September 3 (Xinhua) -- A well-known Ukrainian economist
has praised China's economic development and expressed hope that
China makes further progress after the 15th National Congress of
the Communist Party of China due to be opened on September 12.
</P>
<P>
