<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, September 3 (Xinhua) -- The Provisional Legislature
Council (PLC) of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region (SAR)
today adopted the design of its emblem -- the bauhinia design of
the regional emblem, surrounded by characters in red.
</P>
<P>
