organizers announced today.
</P>
<P>
The festival will be the largest of its kind ever organized in
Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
The Provisional Urban Council, the organizer, said that a total
of 44 performing troupes -- 18 representative groups from the
Chinese mainland and 26 local groups -- will be presenting 34
spectacular indoor as well as 17 free performances.
</P>
<P>
