<HEADLINE> International Educational Equipment Exhibition Opens in Beijing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 3 (Xinhua) -- The Fourth International
Educational Equipment, Instruments and Materials Exhibition opened
here today to showcase the top-level educational accessories from
both at home and abroad.
</P>
<P>
Some 200 manufacturers and trade delegations from China, the
US, Britain and many other countries display over 1,000 kinds of
advanced educational tools at the four-day show, organized by the
China Educational Instrument and Equipment Corporation.
</P>
<P>
Lei Jieqiong, vice-chairman of the National People's Congress
Standing Committee attended the opening ceremony.
</P>
<P>
The exhibition aims to enhance China's cooperation with
developed countries in the field so as to improve the country's
educational resources, the sponsor said.
</P>
<P>
Education experts and scholars worldwide are scheduled to give
a series of lectures under the theme "The Impact of Educational
Equipment on the Development of Education."  
</P>
