in the region following the end of the 20th annual regional summit.
</P>
<P>
The presidents from Costa Rica, Guatemala, Honduras, Nicaragua,
Panama and El Salvador and the prime minister of Belize agreed at
the one-day summit to establish a high-level commission to work
out the conditions for the formation of the union. (Central
America-Summit)
</P>
