chemical manufacturers from the east coast have invested in
Sichuan.
</P>
<P>
In the first half of this year, 73 local electronics, textile,
food and pharmaceutical enterprises had 11.1 billion yuan in sales
and 1.69 billion yuan in profits, up 33 and 54 percent,
respectively, compared with the same period of last year.
</P>
<P>
Sichuan hopes to increase the annual sales of these industries
by 20 percent within three to eight years.  
